## FINDING: at the router-native r=32/64 binarization COLLAPSES separation (bit-gap -1/-2) —
##   the thin ep_wiki margin lived in MAGNITUDE, which sign discards. Recovers at r>=128.
##   r=256 chosen: +19-bit gap, 32-byte sig, power-of-two. Discrete form is STRICTLY weaker
##   than the real dot at equal width; we spend hash width to buy an integer/bit-exact address.

